  "intent": "Perform magnetic bead-based DNA library cleanup for Illumina DNA Prep using automated liquid handling. Transfer 22.5\u00b5L supernatant from magnetic plate to Plate A, add 42.5\u00b5L diluted magnetic beads with 10x mixing, incubate 5 minutes, engage magnet, transfer 62.5\u00b5L to Plate B with mixing. Execute two 200\u00b5L ethanol washes on magnetized beads, remove residual ethanol with 20\u00b5L pipette, add 32\u00b5L RSB buffer, resuspend beads with 12 mix cycles at 25\u00b5L volume, re-engage magnet for 3 minutes, then transfer final 30\u00b5L eluate to Plate C.",
